      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I know about the lines... i've seen them. but they don't change the reality. the reality is that the money is gone, my life is gone, and there's nothing left to rebuild. it's like i've reached the absolute limit of what a person can carry. i'm just... so tired of fighting it. it feels like there is actually no point in trying to climb back out when the pit is this deep.",
